ApproxsimClient.communication
Class SubscriptionHandler

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.communication.SubscriptionHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable
public class SubscriptionHandler
extends Object
implements Runnable

This class handles subscriptions created by differentother objets. It bundles them up in SubscriptionMessages and passes them on to the ServerConnection.
